were families torn apart and countless deaths. Uniquely weaving narrative and historical accounts, DeMare powerfully highlights the often devastating role of fiction in determining history. This corrective retelling ultimately sheds new light on the contemporary legacy of land reform, a legacy fraught with inequality and resentment, but also hope.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mai 2021) 0aCollectivization of agriculturezChinaxHistoryy20th century. 0aCommunism and agriculturezChinaxHistoryy20th century. 0aLand reformzChinaxHistoryy20th century. 0aPropaganda, CommunistzChinaxHistoryy20th century. 0aSocial conflictzChinaxHistoryy20th century. 7aHISTORY / Asia / China.2bisacsh  aChina.  aChinese Communist Party.  aMao Zedong.  aclass.  aland reform.  anarrative.  apeasants.  arevolution.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishz978311070471608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2020 Englishz978311070473008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2020z9783110704525oZDB-23-DEG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUP Complete eBook-Package 2019z978311069228040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978150360952540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781503609525423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9781503609525.jpg  a978-3-11-069228-0  SUP Complete eBook-Package 2019b2019  a978-3-11-070471-6  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishb2020  a978-3-11-070473-0  EBOOK PACKAGE History 2020 Englishb2020  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DEGb2020  aZDB-23-DGGb2020